Installation instructions for C-GLUE-MAKER
------------------------------------------

C-GLUE-MAKER will normally be automatically
installed as part of the system
by the installer.

To install by hand (e.g., if you make
your own modifications), run the

    ./build

script in this directory and then move
the file

    c-glue-maker

to the bin/ directory.

Running ./build requires a properly
functioning installation and
the C-Kit (i.e., Make7 library $ROOT/src/lib/c-kit/src/c-kit-lib.make7).
